result.description:
As described in Task 1.1.1, the deliverable
1) describes the application of the GIF ISAM tool to the pre-conceptual
and conceptual design phases of the ESFR, i.e., QSR and OPT;
2) defines the ESFR safety architecture;
3) defines the associated safety requirements in accordance with the European and international safety framework;
4) analyses the three main safety functions;
5) proposes the list of accidents to be analysed in WP1.2 -- 1.5.
